Package net.ssehub.comani.data

Class ChangedArtifact

java.lang.Object
net.ssehub.comani.data.ChangedArtifact
public class ChangedArtifact
extends java.lang.Object
This class represents a changed artifact as provided by the diff of a commit. Objects of this class always belong to the a specific Commit. They basically provide two lists of strings, from which one contains all lines belonging to the diff header (general information about the artifact, the number of changed lines, etc.) and the other contains the actual contents of the artifact including the changed lines.
Author:
Christian Kroeher
